com.flowpowered.commons.store

Class BinaryFileStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.commons.store.MemoryStore<Integer>
      • com.flowpowered.commons.store.BinaryFileStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SimpleStore<Integer>

    public class BinaryFileStore
extends MemoryStore<Integer>
    This implements a SimpleStore that is stored in memory. The save and load methods can be used to write the map to a binary file.

        public boolean save()
        Description copied from interface: SimpleStore
        Save the map to the persistence system associated with the store. If the store is a memory based volatile map, then this method will have no effect and will always return true.
        Specified by:
